high_descs: Turn to right, go straight to counter, turn left to face counter with tomato, potato, and glass.
Turn left until facing the table. Go forward and turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator. Place potato on top right shelf. Close refrigerator.
Wait 8 seconds. Open refrigerator and remove potato from refrigerator. Close refrigerator. Turn right and go toward table.
anns.task_desc: Move potato from counter to refrigerator, then remove potato from refrigerator and place it on the table.

high_descs: turn right, walk to the counter by the refrigerator
grab the potato on the counter
walk to the right a little
open the refrigerator, put the potato in, cool for a while, take it out
turn right, walk to the table
put the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: cool the potato in the refrigerator, put it on the table

high_descs: Turn right, go forward toward the dishwasher, then turn right face the counter adjacent to the fridge.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Go to the fridge to your right.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Turn right, then move forward to the table.
Put the potato on the table, in front of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato on the table.
